data.eml:eml: A new genus of Neocoelidiinae Oman (Hemiptera: Auchenorrhyncha: Cicadellidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Marques-Costa, Ana Paula, Cavichioli, Rodney Ramiro (2006): A new genus of Neocoelidiinae Oman (Hemiptera: Auchenorrhyncha: Cicadellidae). Zootaxa 1361: 45-51, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.174688
